# BUJA Project Rules

Read `.cursor/rules` for detailed guidelines.

## Quick Rules
1. Minimal context - read only necessary files
2. Tests required for all changes
3. Korean responses, English code comments
4. Update guides when structure changes

## Essential Guides
- `.cursor/CURSOR_GUIDE.md` - Quick reference
- `.cursor/ARCHITECTURE.md` - System design
- `.cursor/DEVELOPMENT.md` - Coding standards

## Large Docs (Reference Only)
- `docs/REQUIREMENTS.md` (503 lines)
- `docs/DESIGN.md` (1719 lines)
